    "Subsequently, it combines its internal knowledge of the world based on its training to provide a comprehensive analysis of speech, language, and communication for the textual transcripts based on quantified measures from part of speech analysis, syntactic phrase identification, semantic analysis (e.g., named entity recognition), and linguistic distribution.",
